 \{\omega \in \Omega \::\: (X+Y)(\omega) \leq x \} \neq \{\omega \in \Omega \::\: X(\omega) \leq x\} \cap \{\omega \in \Omega \::\: Y(\omega) \leq x\}, 
\{\omega \in \Omega \::\: (X+Y)(\omega) \leq x \} = \bigcap_{n \in \mathbb{N}} \{\omega \in \Omega \::\: (X+Y)(\omega) < x +\frac{1}{n} \} \in \mathbb{F}.
